result.title: The Story of MrkZukrbrg
result.content: One day, I came up and talk to God. I asked him, "What is a million years to you?", "A minute." God replied. Seeing an opportune situation, I asked, "Then What is a million dollars to you?", "Only a penny." God said. So I told him, "God... can I have a penny?", God whispered with a devilish smile, "Sure... wait a minute."
